{"tid":2390753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衛稱專家組與中國同行有非常好的討論","createTime":"2021-02-01T18:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T19:48:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b0f0a2aebdedfa5477abee436e06563d73cc7c7f","tid":2390753,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T18:55:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573539-20210202.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573539-20210202.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl4sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=7ba428f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1573539-20210202.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e390e805\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1573539-20210202.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n正在武漢的世衛專家組，昨日到訪湖北省疾控中心，逗留了大約4個半小時。<br />\n<br />\n世衛緊急項目技術主管范科霍夫表示，專家組與中國的同行有非常好的討論，亦計劃到訪武漢病毒研究所等地點，強調要給予專家組一些空間去做科學研究。<br />\n<br />\n世衛緊急項目執行主任瑞安說，世衛會繼續提出問題，亦會要求提供更多數據，認為任何了解疫情大流行如何開始的人，都應該分享資訊。"},{"pid":"e259b9297dc4daec17651c065e67bb45c993fa66","tid":2390753,"uid":83609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T19:02:02.000Z","msg":"討論點作故仔"},{"pid":"6fa1990f1a905b3289145357725ad5c418f1fe76","tid":2390753,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T19:33:36.000Z","msg":"討論源頭屈比意大利, 英國定美國好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744f0a325722710f195cea9f2e6c375a43c4b9ac","tid":2390753,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T19:42:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等睇世衛又俾支共撚"},{"pid":"1fd2c4c8add5575c3d135e8a47cdff99408a8e2f","tid":2390753,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T19:48:01.000Z","msg":"ok 過左數了 幻幻都準備好了 多謝china"},{"pid":"